item.title: About
item.description: Hi, I’m Bhushan. I’m currently working as a Tech Intern at Turtlemint company. I’ve been writing code for about more than 5 years now. I love it, and I hope I will continue doing it. To name a few accomplishments, I’ve been a Google Summer of Code Student at coala organization and have been very good in competitive programming. I was a round 3 qualifier for Google codejam. That’s about it.
